import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]

    plt.plot(data['year'], data['wheat'], label='Wheat Production', color='blue')
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Wheat Production')
    plt.title('What is the trend of wheat production over the years?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.hist(data['wages'], bins=30, color='blue', alpha=0.7, label='Wages')
    plt.axvline(data['wages'].median(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=2, label=f"Median: {data['wages'].median():.2f}")
    plt.xlabel('Wages')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    plt.title('What is the distribution of wages?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    plt.scatter(data['wheat'], data['wages'])
    plt.xlabel('Wheat Production')
    plt.ylabel('Wages')
    plt.title('What is the correlation between wheat production and wages?', wrap=True)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data_grouped = data.groupby('year')['wheat'].mean().reset_index()
    ax = data_grouped.plot.bar(x='year', y='wheat', legend=False)
    plt.title('What is the average wheat production per year?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Average Wheat Production')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)

import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
import pandas as pd

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['year'])]
    
    max_wheat_year = data.loc[data['wheat'].idxmax()]['year'].year
    max_wheat_value = data['wheat'].max()

    plt.bar(data['year'].dt.year, data['wheat'], color='blue', label='Wheat Production')
    plt.axhline(max_wheat_value, color='red', linestyle='--', label=f'Highest Production: {max_wheat_value:.2f}')
    plt.xlabel('Year')
    plt.ylabel('Wheat Production')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the highest wheat production year?', wrap=True)
    
    return plt;

chart = plot(data)
